(2, '面向多种类型大数据的实时检测与深度分析', 2017, 2017, 6, '', '<p>实际完成：\r\n		</p><p>（1）研究面向行业领域大数据的信息融合与深度分析，解决了实时清洗、高度融合、高效存储和索引、分布式大数据挖掘算法、多层次多维度深度分析等关键技术，搭建了新一代智能化行业领域辅助决策平台，实现可视化展示及预测研判。（2）研究面向Web数据进行实体检索与智能分析，设计融合用户社交网络关系的意见挖掘与预测模型框架，提出了细粒度产品属性及意见要素识别与挖掘方法,并完成了实体搜索引擎的架构设计与实现。（3）研究流处理模式下提高实时处理性能的方法，完成了大数据实时处理通用架构设计，并对MapReduce的处理性能进行了优化；基于大数据处理平台完成网络监控系统设计，并对优化算法以及大数据实时处理通用架构进行了验证。\r\n		</p>', 1, 'http://storage.yii2-starter-kit.dev/source', '1/uDnYVr21AMt3D4P8GxFXVGQH3i4eqQIQ.png', '13ZCZDGX01098', NULL, '<p>1.Zhang Y, Zhang W, Gao B, et al. Bid keyword suggestion in sponsored search based on competitiveness and relevance[J]. Information Processing & Management, 2014, 50(4): 508-523.</p>  <p>2.Chen C, Chunyan H, Xiaojie Y. Facet-based trend modeling for cold start of recommendation in social media[C].Orange Technologies (ICOT), 2014 IEEE International Conference on. IEEE, 2014: 125-128.</p>  <p>3.Han S, Cai X, Wang C, et al. Discovery of unique column combinations with hadoop[C]//Asia-Pacific Web Conference. Springer International Publishing, 2014: 533-541.</p>  <p>4.Wang C, Su L, Zhao X, et al. Application performance monitoring and analyzing based on bayesian network[C].Web Information System and Application Conference (WISA), 2014 11th. IEEE, 2014: 61-64.</p>  <p>5.Yuan X, Li X, Yu M, et al. Summarizing relational database schema based on label propagation[C].Asia-Pacific Web Conference. Springer International Publishing, 2014: 258-269.</p>  <p>6.Chen C, Chunyan H O U, Peng N, et al. Personalized Recommendation of Item Category Using Ranking on Time-Aware Graphs[J]. IEICE TRANSACTIONS on Information and Systems, 2015, 98(4): 948-954.</p>  <p>7.Yuan X, Cai X, Yu M, et al. Efficient Foreign Key Discovery Based on Nearest Neighbor Search[C].International Conference on Web-Age Information Management. Springer International Publishing, 2015: 443-447.</p>  <p>8.Yu M, Wang C, Cai X, et al. Overlapping Schema Summarization Based on Multi-label Propagation[C].Asia-Pacific Web Conference. Springer International Publishing, 2015: 352-364.</p>', '<p>一种基于结构概要模型的有向标签图自适应索引构建方法（申请号：201610474116.8）</p><p>跨领域跨类别的新闻评论情绪预测方法（申请号：201410494851.6）</p><p>一种融合多信息源的个性化在线新闻评论情绪预测方法（申请号：201410798427.0）</p><p>一种基于在线医疗问答信息的文本挖掘方法（申请号：CN201510410117.1）</p><p>基于分布式架构的数据流频繁项挖掘算法（申请号：201610254621.1）</p><p>基于GPU加速的kNN算法的网络流量分类方法（申请号：201610258008.7）<br></p>', '<p>南开深海行业领域大数据智能辅助决策平台 （登记号：2016SR245255）</p><p>南开深海大数据多任务调度计算平台（登记号：2016SR150013）</p><p>大数据实时处理通用架构支持的网络监控系统（登记号：2016SR191687）</p>', 'http://10.137.56.40:8080/deepocean/', '1,4'),
